name: current_level
description: The level the data in the row refers to

name: score
description: Score earned in this attempt at the level

name: moves_left
description: The number of moves left to complete the level

name: num_failed_moves
description: Number of illegal moves (the pieces moved back as no match was made)

name: device_model
description: The device used by the player

name: timePlaying
description: Time spent in the level in seconds

name: num_clicks_on_board
description: Number of overall clicks on the board (for any reason)

name: world_serverd
description: Type of world served to the player

name: level_compl_id
description: Unique ID of the sent level completition to be referenced by 'moves' table

name: num_boosters_used
description: How many times the user used a booster
